Class Event

    • Event
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    An Event has a unique identifier. An Event knows when it occured. An Event can remember the distance to where it occured.
